dfischer.utils

Class PerformanceDataRecordBasicFailureMapValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.PerformanceDataRecordBasicFailureMapValue

  • public class PerformanceDataRecordBasicFailureMapValue
extends java.lang.Object
    Value-object for the PerformanceDataRecordBasicFailureMap. Contains an arraylist of failure times for failed URL calls with similar status types and a HTTP status codes.
    See Also:
    PerformanceDataRecordBasicFailureMap
